<lb n="0071a21"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0071001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西天譯經三藏＝宋【明】</note><app n="0071001"><lem>西天譯經三藏</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋</rdg></app>朝散大夫試鴻臚卿
<lb n="0071a22"/><note n="0071002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">傳＝明【明】【宋】</note><app n="0071002"><lem>傳</lem><rdg wit="【明】【宋】" resp="Taisho">明</rdg></app>教大師<note n="0071003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臣法賢＝法天【明】</note><app n="0071003"><lem>臣法賢</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">法天</rdg></app>奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0071a23"/><lg><l>歸命佛法僧</l><l>頂禮觀自在</l>
<lb n="0071a24"/><l>我今稱讚彼</l><l>大悲功德林</l></lg></div1>
